Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(350,340)}{\fn黑体\be1}{\bord2}淡雪舰队旗舰 巡查舰杰姆卡乌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(350,340)}{\fn黑体\be1}{\bord2}亚布人类帝国 帝都拉克法卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要说的话 是如同生命般 无可替代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 彼此仍装作没有发觉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿让你看见 波涛澎湃的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.57,0:23:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一缕发丝摇曳 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咽下那句话 I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.96,0:24:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FareWell my love 觉察之时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.35,0:24:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to go 即为别离之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強いて言えば命と同じ　かけがえないひととわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それでもお互い　気づかないふりして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見せたくない　波立つ心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.57,0:23:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髪をひとつゆすり 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲み込んだ　I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.96,0:24:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell my love　気づいた時は
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.35,0:24:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to go　別れの時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
